    viewAll: "View all frequently asked questions",
    items: [{"q":"How long does it take to set up my LLC?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">Your LLC is formed in less than 5 days.</strong> It's one of the fastest processes in the world to open an international company.</p><p class=\"mb-3\">What you receive in that timeframe:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">State certificate of formation (Articles of Organization)</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Provisional EIN to start operating and open accounts</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Custom Operating Agreement and US business address</div></div><p>We then handle the ITIN and bank account opening — with your business already invoicing.</p>"},
{"q":"What is an LLC and why should I care if I invoice online?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\">An LLC (<strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">Limited Liability Company</strong>) is an American company that pays no corporate taxes in the US if you have no physical presence there.</p><p class=\"mb-3\">For digital entrepreneurs who invoice online from anywhere in the world, it's the most efficient structure because it gives you access to:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">American banking and international payment gateways</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Legal protection of your personal assets</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">An optimized tax base</div></div><p>All without setting foot in the United States.</p>"},{"q":"Is it legal to optimize my taxes with a US LLC?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">Completely legal.</strong> The United States allows any person from any country to form an LLC.</p><p class=\"mb-3\">Tax optimization is not evasion: it consists of choosing the legal structure that allows you to pay what's fair according to current laws.</p><p>Thousands of Spanish-speaking digital entrepreneurs already operate with US LLCs in a completely legal and transparent way.</p>"},{"q":"Do I need to travel to the United States to set up the LLC?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">No.</strong> The entire process is 100% online:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">LLC formation</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">EIN obtainment from the IRS</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Bank account opening</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Complete documentation</div></div><p>You don't need to set foot in the United States now or ever. You can be in Spain, Argentina, Mexico or any other country and have your LLC operational in less than 15 days.</p>"},{"q":"How long does the entire process take?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\">From confirmation to having your LLC formed and bank account operational, it usually takes between <strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">7 and 15 business days</strong>.</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">Formation:</strong> between 3 and 5 days depending on the state</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">Bank account:</strong> between 24 hours and one week</div></div><p>We coordinate everything in parallel to make it as fast as possible.</p>"},{"q":"What happens after forming the LLC? Do you leave me on my own?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\"><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">No.</strong> An LLC has annual obligations with the IRS and the state where it's registered:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Form 1120 + Form 5472 with the IRS</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Registered Agent renewal</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">BOI Report</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Annual Report (in states that require it)</div></div><p>Our annual maintenance service covers all of this. We keep the calendar, prepare the forms and file them for you. We don't disappear after formation.</p>"},{"q":"How do I know if an LLC makes sense for my situation?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\">Book a <strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">free 30-minute Exentax consultation</strong>. In that call:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">We analyze your business model and income</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">We review your country of residence and objectives</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">We tell you with total honesty if an LLC makes sense for you or not</div></div><p>If it doesn't, we'll tell you without any problem. We gain nothing from setting up something you don't need.</p>"},{"q":"Can I have the LLC and still be self-employed in my country?","a":"<p class=\"mb-3\">It depends on your specific situation. Many of our clients maintain a <strong class=\"text-[var(--text-1)]\">hybrid structure</strong>:</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 mt-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">The LLC for international invoicing</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[rgba(0,229,16,0.32)] px-4 py-2.5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-1)] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(11,13,12,0.04)]\">Their local entity for domestic operations</div></div><p>Others migrate completely to the LLC. Each case is different and we analyze it in the initial call to find the optimal configuration.</p>"}]
