      items: [{"q":"What does the incorporation service include exactly?","paragraphs":["It includes everything needed to create and launch your LLC in the United States.","We handle the entire process so the company is correctly incorporated and ready to operate.","The service includes:"],"list":["Legal LLC incorporation in the selected state","Official state formation fees","EIN application with the IRS","Registered Agent for the first year","BOI Report filing with FinCEN","Assistance with opening a business bank account","Initial support to configure payments and payment gateways"],"note":"The price is fixed from the start. No hidden costs or unexpected surcharges."},{"q":"How long does it take to have my LLC ready?","paragraphs":["Incorporation is usually completed in 2 to 4 business days, depending on the state.","The IRS EIN may take a few additional days, as it depends on the IRS's own processing times.","Once everything is approved, we deliver the complete documentation so you can start operating."],"list":[],"note":""},{"q":"Why is there a price difference between states?","paragraphs":["Each state has different official fees and different maintenance obligations.","New Mexico offers an efficient structure for operating internationally without unnecessary complexity.","Wyoming and Delaware have somewhat higher costs, but offer additional advantages in privacy or more complex corporate structures.","During the initial consultation we help you choose the state that really makes sense for your case."],"list":[],"note":""},{"q":"Do I have to pay maintenance from the first year?","paragraphs":["No.","The first year of Registered Agent is already included in the incorporation price.","Annual maintenance starts from the second year, when it is necessary to renew the registered agent and file the corresponding compliance obligations."],"list":[],"note":""},{"q":"What happens if I don't file the mandatory forms?","paragraphs":["An LLC with a foreign owner must file certain informational forms with the IRS, such as Form 5472.","If they are not filed correctly, the IRS may impose significant penalties for non-compliance.","That's why we offer an annual maintenance service that handles these filings and monitors the filing deadlines."],"list":[],"note":""},{"q":"Does it include my tax declaration in my home country?","paragraphs":["No.","Our service focuses on the LLC's incorporation and compliance with its US obligations.","Your personal declaration in your country of residence must be handled with your local tax advisor, as it depends on your personal situation and the regulations in your country.","If your advisor needs information about your LLC, we can provide all the necessary documentation."],"list":[],"note":""}]
